{"tid":1639114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母垃撚圾黨鐵 宵禁搞到銀髮族差d訓街","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:02:11.000Z","uid":276392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dda3999785372cea7e723ab105f46662de2820d0","tid":1639114,"uid":276392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"今日全世界都知8點停黨鐵<br />\n但大西北接駁巴士kxx 個d好似無預告都會停（可能我miss左喇）<br />\n岩放工番到大西北 諗住等平時架接駁巴士番屋企<br />\n點知個垃圾app keep 住update 到站時間但原來八點已經停撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我後生我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁班銀髮族呢？<br />\n佢地好多都唔識用smart phone 就算識都唔一定識用個垃圾黨鐵app！<br />\n<br />\n咁岩有兩個銀髮族都等緊車 我就多口問佢地係咪番 XX村 原來佢地係住我附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁跟手就帶住佢地搵的士 到最後要用app call先搵到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試問一對七八十歲既銀髮族唔識用電話唔識call車番唔到屋企 係咪要係條街流連 訓街等到第二日開車？<br />\n<br />\n就算有仔女都唔會立刻係佢地身邊幫到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n垃圾黨鐵同柒婆我屌撚哂你地老母臭閪 割你老豆春袋單春雞<br />\n宵你老母系禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699c67c904a58a84769a73de90f2f9142530b960","tid":1639114,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:53:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e59a3a4b642c2cdda866bd5d7d0682f08be47456","tid":1639114,"uid":276392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"699c67c904a58a84769a73de90f2f9142530b960","tid":1639114,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:53: